Patient Tracking & Scheduling System

This is a simple web-based prototype designed to manage patients and appointments.

How to Run:
1. Download or open the repository
2. Navigate to the 1_code folder
3. Open index.html in any web browser

Features:
- Add patient information
- View patient list
- Schedule appointments
- View scheduled appointments
- Data stored using browser local storage

This system demonstrates basic functionality of a patient tracking and scheduling system.
